headline: AI Agents and the Jobs Report Jitter: A Wall Street Balancing Act
summary: Wall Street paused its recent rally as a robust January jobs report cooled expectations for a swift Federal Reserve pivot, while the burgeoning "AI agent" narrative sent shockwaves through the software sector, creating a stark divide between winners and losers.
